            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Hic requiescit in <lb n="2"/>pace Innocentius <lb n="3"/>qui deprecans s<expan><ex>an</ex><abbr>c</abbr><ex>tae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>emoriae</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Andream et s<expan><ex>an</ex><abbr>c</abbr><ex>tae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>emoriae</ex></expan> Do<lb break="no" n="5"/>natum et s<expan><ex>an</ex><abbr>c</abbr><ex>tae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>nimae</ex></expan> Iusti<lb break="no" n="6"/><expan><abbr>na</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> ut si quis ista se<lb break="no" n="7"/>pultura <expan><abbr>pos</abbr><ex>t</ex></expan> depos<lb break="no" n="8"/><expan><abbr>itione</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> eius aperire v<lb break="no" n="9"/>oluerit vel iusserit <lb n="10"/>aperire iudicium ves<lb break="no" n="11"/>trum puniatur
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Hedera am Ende von Z. 11 (B): AE 1983: Z. 2: pace IN(!) Innocentius; Z. 5/6: Iustina(m).</p>
            </div>
